Package dataAccess

Class Accessor<ModelType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • dataAccess.Accessor<ModelType>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AuthTokenAccessor, EventAccessor, PersonAccessor, UserAccessor
    public abstract class Accessor<ModelType>
extends java.lang.Object
    A generic Accessor class that defines the base for all Accessors. It guarantees basic database manupulation operations for a given model type, however subclasses should implement more functions as needed (ex. database query functions)
